
eProcurement 

The purpose of this e-mail is to invite you to a demonstration of the new 
eProcurement system and to provide you additional learning information. 

See the New eProcurement System
When?
Thursday, June 14  
11:00 AM - 12:30 PM for Enron Net Works personnel  
12:30 PM - 2:00 PM for Corporate and EWS personnel with Enron Americas, Enron 
Industrial Markets, and Enron Global Markets
(Lunch will not be provided.)
Where?
The Forum on Floor 12 of Two Allen Center
What will I see?
The iBuyit team will walk you through various request scenarios and highlight 
new eProcurement features, including the new approval routing process.  
Who should attend?
Current eProcurement users who were unable to attend the Brown Bag on May 31 
or who do not plan on participating in future eProcurement training. 
How do I sign up?
Please respond to this e-mail and indicate which session you plan to attend.

Calendar of Additional Learning Opportunities
The attached calendar details upcoming online training, demos, and classroom 
instruction.  These activities are targeted to new eProcurement users.  

